data.description: PARKING PASS REQUIRED...ASK REALTOR FOR INSTRUCTIONS! Renovated Interior Throughout:  Bathrooms! Modern lighting and chandelier in eat in kitchen! 1-inch and 2-inch blinds! Granite countertops, Double sink, Single wand faucet, luxury vinyl and hardwood flooring throughout, Berber carpet on stairways! Solid wrought iron security door! Brand new gas furnace and A/C system 3 years old! All Appliances 3 years old! Updated closet systems! Hardwood Railings! Plus near all major DC attractions and military bases (within 10-45 minute drives). Check out these Grant/Loan Programs: ONE+, Majority Minority Census Track Program, Journey Home Grant and the Welcome Home Grant.
